OL,3,CReason for major IT crash at major
OL,4,Chospitals not known
OL,6,FThe ramifications of the major IT
OL,7,Fcrash across the Southern Health Trust
OL,8,Flast week are still being felt, as
OL,9,Furgent attempts are made to reschedule
OL,10,Fmore than 1,600 procedures and
OL,11,Fappointments.
OL,13,FOn Monday the health minister told
OL,14,FMLAs that questions over why the
OL,15,Fsystem failed remain unanswered with
OL,16,FMike Nesbitt admitting he is concerned
OL,17,Fthat it could happen again.
