OL,3,CReason for major IT crash at major
OL,4,Chospitals not known
OL,6,FLast Wednesday a major incident was
OL,7,Fdeclared at sites across the Southern
OL,8,FHealth trust with patients being
OL,9,Fwarned to not attend appointments at
OL,10,Fany hospital or community service in
OL,11,Fthe area.
OL,13,FDaisy Hill Hospital in Newry and
OL,14,FCraigavon Area Hospital were among the
OL,15,Ftrust facilitates affected.
OL,17,FThey urged any other patients to avoid
OL,18,Fcoming to any of its hospitals until
OL,19,Ffurther notice.
