OL,3,CReason for major IT crash at major
OL,4,Chospitals not known
OL,6,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt faced
OL,7,Fintense questioning in the Assembly on
OL,8,FMonday following the system failure.
OL,10,FSpeaking about the incident, he
OL,11,Fadmitted that he still wasn't clear on
OL,12,Fwhy the crash occurred or why the
OL,13,Fbackup systems had also malfunctioned.
OL,15,F"We know what happened, there was a
OL,16,Fplanned software upgrade that went
OL,17,Fwrong," Mr Nesbitt told Assembly
OL,18,Fmembers. "But we still don't know why
OL,19,Fit went wrong."
