OL,6,FHe added that he was "particularly
OL,7,Finterested" in understanding why both
OL,8,Fthe primary and backup data centres
OL,9,Ffailed simultaneously, a situation he
OL,10,Fdescribed as "deeply concerning."
OL,12,F"If a backup system falls along with
OL,13,Fthe primary one, it defeats its very
OL,14,Fpurpose."
OL,16,FThe major incident led to ambulances
OL,17,Fbeing diverted to other emergency
OL,18,Fdepartments with mutual aid from
OL,19,Fneighbouring trusts initiated to help
OL,20,Fmanage the impact.
