OL,6,FHowever, the ripple effects are still
OL,7,Fpresent with over 1,600 procedures
OL,8,Fpostponed, as the minister warned even
OL,9,Fmore patients could be affected in the
OL,10,Fcoming days.
OL,12,FHe said: "There will be clinical
OL,13,Fdecisions made regarding those whose
OL,14,Fprocedures were postponed, and this
OL,15,Fwill unfortunately have a knock-on
OL,16,Feffect on others currently waiting for
OL,17,Ftreatment."
