OL,6,FWhen asked whether similar IT failures
OL,7,Fcould happen in other health trusts,
OL,8,FMr Nesbitt admitted there was concern:
OL,9,F"That concern will remain until I am
OL,10,Fsatisfied that we now know not just
OL,11,Fwhat happened, but why it happened."
OL,13,FDUP MLA Diane Dodds raised further
OL,14,Fconcerns in the Assembly, revealing
OL,15,Fthat the system had reportedly gone
OL,16,Fdown for several hours earlier in the
OL,17,Fmonth.
OL,19,FMr Nesbitt said he had been unaware of
OL,20,Fthat incident but promised to
OL,21,Finvestigate.
